+ * SDEI (Software Delegated Exception Interface) client for Xen
+ * Implements Physical SDEI Client role (EL2 receiving from EL3 Firmware)
+ *
+ * Per ARM DEN0054C 
+ * Copyright (C) 2026 Ahmed Wafdy ahmedadelwafdy782@gmail.com
